[normal]Written evidence submitted from [bold]Quality of Life Association[bold]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;[bold]1.1 Quality of Life 
[normal](QLA) 
[normal]was the first Lao Civil 
[normal]S
[normal]ociety 
[normal]O
[normal]rganisation to provide assistance and support to 
[normal]unexploded ordinance (
[normal]UXO
[normal])
[normal] survivors in Lao PDR as well as to people with disabilities. In its daily activities, QLA sees the barriers 
[normal]that people with disabilities (
[normal]PWD
[normal])
[normal], including survivors, are facing
[normal],
[normal] and tries 
[normal]to 
[normal] break them down to empower PWD and develop opportunities for them to participate 
[normal]fully in 
[normal]society
